It's like the youth project at the church trying to finish the rest of that.

00:46:46.783 --> 00:46:47.137
I think they need another, like, $200,000 or something more.

00:46:47.137 --> 00:46:51.707
So, if you're in a small community, $200,000 is a lot of money.

00:46:51.707 --> 00:46:52.697
Do you get that?

00:47:01.200 --> 00:47:01.600
So you get a little bit here, you get a little bit there, and you're excited whenever you get enough to be able to put some cement slabs up or whatever.

00:47:01.600 --> 00:47:04.022
But I thought, what does it take to be a paymaster?

00:47:04.022 --> 00:47:09.880
What does it take to be that person that has the big money, like the Greens?

00:47:09.880 --> 00:47:16.594
If it wasn't for the Greens of Hobby Lobby, ORU wouldn't exist right now.

00:47:24.236 --> 00:47:24.400
The Holy Spirit used them.

00:47:38.600 --> 00:47:38.800
And some people get ticked off at people being, you know, they say, 'F the rich' and all this craziness, whatever.

00:47:38.800 --> 00:47:40.000
I mean, it's so ignorant.

00:47:40.000 --> 00:47:48.460
If it wasn't for the Greens being used by the Holy Spirit, ORU would have closed their doors.

00:47:48.460 --> 00:47:54.613
I think they had to give them $47 million or they would have closed their doors because of mismanagement of money.

00:47:54.613 --> 00:48:03.840
There had to be something, but it was them bailing them out that God used to help save that whole university.

00:48:03.840 --> 00:48:05.736
And my wife graduated there, thank God.

00:48:05.736 --> 00:48:08.120
Thank God, it is a Christian university.

00:48:08.120 --> 00:48:09.920
