00:48:09.920 --> 00:48:18.680
But the Lord showed me a major revival is about to happen there.

00:48:18.680 --> 00:48:32.400
But it took somebody with some common sense that had 400 stores, Hobby Lobbies, and Mardel's all throughout the United States that was able to say, 'Here, here's a $47 million check.

00:48:32.400 --> 00:48:39.540
' I don't know about you, but even a million-dollar check, I'd pass out.

00:48:39.540 --> 00:48:40.800
$100,000, you know, come on.

00:48:40.800 --> 00:48:45.794
But 47 million bucks here, do you—that is an absurd amount of money.

00:48:45.794 --> 00:48:47.840
That's crazy money.

00:48:47.840 --> 00:48:51.160
But they had it, and I thought we need more people like that.

00:48:51.160 --> 00:49:00.950
But what is it going to take to get that?

00:49:00.950 --> 00:49:05.840
First, the love of money is the root of all evil.

00:49:05.840 --> 00:49:20.440
If you're crazy about money and God can't get it through you, He won't get it to you.

00:49:20.440 --> 00:49:42.880
So, I really truly believe there's something more to this for the end-time harvest and the end-time wealth transfer for what we need for these next couple of months and going into the next year.

00:50:03.290 --> 00:50:03.695
I heard one pastor talking about how we're about to have an economic crisis.

00:51:12.680 --> 00:51:13.060
I believe there's an outpouring of finances first.

00:51:35.800 --> 00:51:36.000
And that's what I believe for the body of Christ, that we lack nothing.

00:51:36.000 --> 00:52:15.030
We should not be lacking anything.

00:52:15.040 --> 00:52:29.118
We need this to get the job done.

00:52:29.118 --> 00:52:43.680
So, I think about things all the time.

00:52:52.480 --> 00:52:56.000
I pray and the Lord gives me these ideas.

00:52:56.000 --> 00:53:07.547
I'm driving down the road and He'll say, 'That land over there.

00:53:07.547 --> 00:53:51.280
If somebody buys that, they'll be able to, and within the next couple of months, that land's going to quadruple in price and it'd be worth millions.

00:53:51.280 --> 00:54:00.320
' But that takes money to buy that.

00:54:00.320 --> 00:54:06.370
But He's always educating me.

00:54:06.370 --> 00:54:20.080
He's always teaching me about the end-time harvest money.

00:54:20.080 --> 00:54:37.520
He teaches me all the time and He talks to me, and I know something's about to happen.

00:54:37.520 --> 00:54:42.670
I know.

00:54:42.680 --> 00:55:08.958
I just believe it because I'm like, 'Why are you telling me this stuff?

00:55:10.315 --> 00:55:16.130
Are you just educating me?

00:55:16.130 --> 00:55:30.158
' Practicing His presence—people go, 'What's that mean, Brandon?

00:55:30.158 --> 00:55:44.110
What does that mean to practice His presence?

00:55:44.110 --> 00:55:54.040
' Act like He's there.

00:57:09.720 --> 00:57:09.860
I don't look at God as twinkle, twinkle, little star.

00:57:09.860 --> 00:57:11.886
'Lord, you're way out there somewhere where you are.

00:57:11.886 --> 00:57:13.800
' He's in me.

00:57:13.800 --> 00:57:14.949
He dwells.

00:57:14.949 --> 00:57:18.520
As He is, so are we in this world.

00:57:30.640 --> 00:57:31.040
I act like He's just like my wife sitting next to me.

00:57:31.040 --> 00:57:32.880
'Hey, how's your day?

00:57:36.264 --> 00:57:36.548
I love you.

00:57:54.880 --> 00:57:55.195
I want to talk to you.

00:57:55.195 --> 00:57:56.770
Are you my friend?

00:57:56.770 --> 00:58:05.420
' When I told you I ticked Him off yesterday, I knew it immediately because my broadcast was terrible.

00:58:05.800 --> 00:58:09.360
And I said, 'Lord, why is this so bad?

00:58:09.360 --> 00:58:17.630
' He said, 'Your attitude's bad, and I'm not going to pour that cloak on you.

00:58:20.260 --> 00:58:20.520
It's teaching you.

00:58:57.520 --> 00:58:58.440
You cannot have that.

00:58:58.440 --> 00:59:03.690
You've got to repent and go on.

00:59:03.690 --> 00:59:38.184
' And the moment I fixed it—but it caused me to align because, bottom line, folks, I was irritated because there were so many of you all irritated that came to the meeting that wanted to talk to me and I didn't know how to handle it, and there were things that I had to deal with in my heart about it.

00:59:47.133 --> 00:59:51.410
And the Lord instructed me because I didn't know what to do.

00:59:51.410 --> 00:59:53.053
I'm new at this.

00:59:53.053 --> 01:00:25.540
I'm just a dude that's just getting raised up in ministry, and I'm just telling you all, I don't have all the answers and I'm asking the Holy Spirit, 'You teach me.

01:00:25.540 --> 01:00:28.080
I need you.

01:00:28.080 --> 01:00:30.320
I don't know what to do.

01:00:30.320 --> 01:00:46.751
' And as I grow, and I've seen my elders, you know, that have been in this for 50 years...

01:00:46.751 --> 01:00:48.213
like a widow woman.

01:00:48.213 --> 01:01:01.360
She was a widow raising up four kids by herself without a husband.

01:01:13.378 --> 01:01:29.653
He died at 48 years old, 49 years old, and she raised kids up all that rest of that time by herself and had them and everything, and God used her.

01:01:29.920 --> 01:01:34.912
And she carried a ministry without a husband all those years.

01:01:34.912 --> 01:01:36.000
And there's something to learn about that.

01:01:36.000 --> 01:01:37.560
That's honorable.

01:01:38.485 --> 01:01:47.400
I can't imagine, usually, a woman doing something by herself without a husband back there beside her to help do it.

01:01:53.206 --> 01:01:55.651
I know Kathryn Kuhlman did some things, but she was married at some point in time.

01:02:08.027 --> 01:02:08.440
But there's something to be said about that.

01:02:08.440 --> 01:02:11.920
Longevity in ministry is not an easy thing.

01:02:11.920 --> 01:02:14.622
I've seen them come and I've seen them go.

01:02:29.680 --> 01:02:30.320
You see a spark and you go, 'What happened to them?

01:02:30.320 --> 01:02:34.510
There was an anointing on them one time, but they're gone.

01:02:34.510 --> 01:02:41.645
' But when you say, 'I've been in ministry and I'm a female and I've been doing this for 40, 50 years, whatever.

01:02:41.645 --> 01:02:43.465
How long has yours been?

01:02:43.465 --> 01:02:48.876
' you should pay attention because they're doing something where they beat the odds.

01:02:49.418 --> 01:02:51.991
It's like you watch somebody and they've played chess perfectly.

01:02:51.991 --> 01:02:52.898
'How did you do that?

01:02:52.898 --> 01:02:57.147
' Only by the grace of God, by the glory of God.

01:02:57.147 --> 01:02:58.170
That's not normal.

01:02:58.170 --> 01:03:00.448
