01:03:56.715 --> 01:04:06.313
It's the truth.

01:04:06.313 --> 01:04:19.170
I listen to them and I go, 'There's something so deep.

01:04:19.170 --> 01:04:27.280
' I know they don't talk a lot.

01:04:27.280 --> 01:04:33.420
These elders don't talk a lot.

01:04:33.420 --> 01:04:34.800
They don't.

01:04:34.800 --> 01:04:38.087
So, I pull from them.

01:04:48.489 --> 01:04:48.764
