01:07:41.610 --> 01:07:52.480
' It's easy to get it and have it for a little bit, but to keep it and sustain it for decades, I don't know.

01:07:53.880 --> 01:08:03.260
I just tell you all my little things that I'm thinking about.

01:08:55.080 --> 01:08:55.448
That's my thing before I pray.

01:09:11.920 --> 01:09:13.088
I try to pull you along my road that I'm going down.

01:09:13.088 --> 01:09:18.175
I'm just really open and honest with y'all.

01:09:44.080 --> 01:10:21.464
You know, I don't have it all figured out, but I watch the elders and I watch the people and I listen to their conversations, and I think about what they think about going on because I know what the Father has told me I'm going to do and I don't have a clue how I'm going to get there.

01:10:21.464 --> 01:10:25.733
